      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHISKEY WHISKERS (1) struggled to get involved last start after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won easily by 6 lengths at Geelong (25.63) beating Doongalla Don in a Mix 4/5 H on July 10. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. LIKE A ROCK (5) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from six tries. Was out of the placings last time (30.24) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. Can feature in the finish. NOVA OWEN (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (30.13) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at The Meadows. Can improve sharply here. FLAMING SMOOTH (7) hit the frame latest (30.79) when third at The Meadows in a Grade 5. Has already won two times from this draw.",
